## Ignore Visual Studio temporary files, build results, and
## files generated by popular Visual Studio add-ons.
##
## Get latest from https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/master/VisualStudio.gitignore


**/.vs/
**/obj/
**/bin/
*.exe
*.pdb
*.manifest
*.cache


